messages.messageBody:
**Carol, how goes the move?**

Slow ! We bought land in VA ( 18 acres !!). Can't move until we sell the house :(

Anyone interested in moving to Maine ? ;) How cool would that be ....... having an unschooling family buy here ? I wanna go south ( whine whine whine ;) We'd definitely be able to get to the conference easier.

Carol

messages.messageBody:
I'm leaving for the Live and Learn conference tomorrow afternoon. I
work all morning and go straight to the airport after work, so
probably won't be on here for a while. Hope all is well with everyone
and I'll try to check in from the conference site.

Take care everyone!

Ren
